| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-2357 — Recovery Inhibition (qilin)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 9ee01ab8-0da2-54da-96b1-b821f43c39e3"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
